# Test Agent Smith APIs
# Simple REST client tests for the orchestrator and worker

### Check Worker Health
GET http://localhost:8002/health

###

### Take Screenshot
POST http://localhost:8002/screenshot
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Screen Size
GET http://localhost:8002/screen_size

###

### Get Mouse Position
GET http://localhost:8002/mouse_position

###

### Execute Action - Move Mouse
POST http://localhost:8002/action
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "move",
  "x": 500,
  "y": 300
}

###

### Execute Action - Click
POST http://localhost:8002/action
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "click",
  "button": "left"
}

###

### Reset Session
POST http://localhost:8002/reset_session

###

### Check Orchestrator
GET http://localhost:8010/

###

### Get All Runs
GET http://localhost:8010/runs

###

### Create New Run
POST http://localhost:8010/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Test mouse movement and click"
}

###

### Get Run Details (replace {run_id} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8010/runs/{run_id}

###

### Approve Step (replace IDs with actual values)
POST http://localhost:8010/runs/{run_id}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "step_id": "{step_id}"
}

###

### Reject Step (replace IDs with actual values)
POST http://localhost:8010/runs/{run_id}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "step_id": "{step_id}"
}

###

### Get Settings
GET http://localhost:8010/settings

###

### Update Settings
POST http://localhost:8010/settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "approval",
  "rate_limit": 2,
  "step_timeout": 60
}

###
